{"id":232746189,"title":"#分享 完美的二頭肌訓練 (中文字幕)","content":"http://i.imgur.com/9lFUMpD.jpg\n\nhttp://bit.ly/2sdWLNB\n\n \n這次的訓練內容介紹如何充分訓練到二頭肌，整理成一套完整的訓練內容，為了要充分訓練到二頭肌，要挑選特定的訓練動作，必須要針對六種不同的訓練要素加強，要能夠讓手旋後、肘屈曲、肩屈曲，同時在動作最初以及中間還有最後提升肌肉所承受的張力。\n\n完美的二頭肌訓練\n\n1A. 槓鈴作弊彎舉 3組做到力竭\n1B. 槓鈴滑式彎舉 做到力竭\n\n2A. 負重的反手引體向上 3組做到力竭\n2B. 頂峰收縮的反手彎舉 做到力竭\n\n以上每兩個訓練動作，都要用遞減訓練法來做\n\n3. 彈力帶的啞鈴彎舉 3組做到力竭\n\n4. 啞鈴上斜彎舉 3組做到力竭(伸展反射)\n\n5. 啞鈴彎舉三重奏 2組(每隻手在每種動作都要做8下)\n\n \n--\nFitting Room TW\n運動、健康相關資訊翻譯影片\n官方Blog\nhttp://fittingroomtw.blogspot.tw/\n官方臉書\nhttps://goo.gl/HZhAhS","excerpt":"這次的訓練內容介紹如何充分訓練到二頭肌，整理成一套完整的訓練內容，為了要充分訓練到二頭肌，要挑選特定的訓練動作，必須要針對六種不同的訓練要素加強，要能夠讓手旋後、肘屈曲、肩屈曲，同時在動作最初以及中間","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"9b5213d6-4427-4a3c-b788-efa19493631c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-23T14:37:16.304Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-23T14:37:16.304Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["二頭肌","健身"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"健身","forumAlias":"fitness","school":"FRTW","department":"fittingroomtw","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/9lFUMpD.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"e936a760-aee3-40b7-8caf-1f73883db17d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/9lFUMpDl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/9lFUMpDl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/9lFUMpDl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-23T14:37:16.304Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-23T14:37:16.304Z"},{"id":"e936a760-aee3-40b7-8caf-1f73883db17d","url":"http://i.imgur.com/9lFUMpD.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/9lFUMpD","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/9lFUMpDl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"create